{
  "text": "For convenience, one may extend p i to the entire graph by setting p i ( x, y) = 0 whenever x or y \u2208 X \\ D i . By maximum principle arguments it follows that p i \u2192 p monotonically as i \u2192 \u221e, see [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] for more details.",
  "correct_citation": {
